the hitcher is a 1986 american road action-horror film directed by robert harmon and written by eric red . it stars rutger hauer , c. thomas howell , jennifer jason leigh , and jeffrey demunn . howell plays jim , a young man who gives a ride to a hitchhiker , played by hauer . after narrowly escaping death , jim repeatedly encounters the hitchhiker , who is revealed to be a serial killer , and the two engage in a game of cat and mouse . it was released in the united states on february 21 , 1986 .